478Likes
127,209Views
Nov 282025
Hong Kong firefighters found dozens more bodies in an intensive search of a highrise complex where a massive fire engulfed seven buildings, bringing the death toll to 128 with many more unaccounted for. Authorities arrested another eight people involved in the towers' renovation.
